description: L1 absence, L2 first occurrence of actual sampled section, L3 first occurrence of riff created from sampled section. Sampled section is only one bar – riff used in sample track is two bars consisting of full sampled section, then first half of the bar played twice. In other words, 8 beats, consisting of beats 1 2 3 4 1 2 1 2 from the sampled section in the ref track
